<h1>Edit Post</h1>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <p>Guidelines for posting</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Make sure it rhymes.</li>
      <li>Do't use the letter "A".</li>
      <li>The incessant use of hashtags will get you insta-banned.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-8">
    <%= render partial: 'form', locals: { topic: @topic, post: @post } %>
  </div>
</div>
